channel.title: Newton Faulkner
channel.description:
I'm enjoying his music at the moment. Been jamming with mates so some of it, spruced it up a bit. It's great to experiment with. If you get time, check him out. Don't just listen to dream catch me, because it's his most famous, try some others. I recommend tearp drop and uncomfortably slow. If you get around to it, tell me what you think.
Syrillia
